	BK Technologies | BK Two-way Radio Communications	












BK Technologies | BK Two-way Radio Communications






























 




























































 






















 








RELM Wireless is re-branding as BK Technologies to emphasize and focus on its flagship product, BK Radio, and to incorporate a comprehensive product offering around the BK Radio brand to the public safety marketplace. Our vision is to expand upon and encompass a broader market perspective on the long-established BK Radio brand.  





INTRODUCING BK TECHNOLOGIES
		

RELM Wireless to Rebrand as BK Technologies
		










RELM Wireless is re-branding as BK Technologies to emphasize and focus on its flagship product, BK Radio, and to incorporate a comprehensive product offering around the BK Radio brand to the public safety marketplace. Our vision is to expand upon and encompass a broader market perspective on the long-established BK Radio brand.  





INTRODUCING BK TECHNOLOGIES
		

RELM Wireless to Rebrand as BK Technologies
		


 


 

 

BK TechnologiesBlacktie2017-07-17T15:46:20+00:00 
BK Technologies About BK Technologies
As an American manufacturer for 70 years, BK Technologies is deeply rooted in the public safety communications industry, manufacturing high-specification communications equipment of unsurpassed reliability and value for use by public safety professionals and government agencies. Advances include a broad new line of leading digital two‑way radios compliant with APCO Project 25 specifications. BK Technologies’ products are manufactured and distributed worldwide under BK Radio and RELM brand names. The Company maintains its headquarters in West Melbourne, Florida and can be contacted through its web site at www.bktechnologies.com or directly at 1-800-821-2900. The Company’s common stock trades on the NYSE MKT market under the symbol “RWC”.    

PUBLIC SAFETY
We build high spec P25
reliable communications, keeping our cities connected
and our communities safe.

 

BUSINESS & INDUSTRIAL
Construction, security, hotels, hospitals…
we’ve got your communications covered.

 

FEDERAL GOVERNMENT
BK Radios are in the hands of many
Federal Agencies and Departments and proudly
work alongside those who make a difference.

 
